<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <title>HerpetologyPro | <%= yield :title %></title>
  <meta name="description" value="HerpID teaches people to identify reptiles and amphibians">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
  <%= csp_meta_tag %>
  <%= javascript_pack_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
  <script src="https://unpkg.com/popper.js@1.15.0/dist/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-L2pyEeut/H3mtgCBaUNw7KWzp5n9+4pDQiExs933/5QfaTh8YStYFFkOzSoXjlTb" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
<!--  <script src="https://unpkg.com/@tippy.js/react@2.2.3/umd/index.min.js" integrity="sha384-n7roSqy7Dx4XuyE6PqRsmJx2Rh0K0shH6F9Tah9ruDvMwgn+Pq25XW3Oi0s9j9dH" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>-->
</head>
  <script async src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=UA-111016820-5"></script>
  <script>window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];

  function gtag() { dataLayer.push(arguments); }
  gtag('js', new Date());
  gtag('config', 'UA-111016820-5');</script>

<body><div id="logo-holder">
  <div id="logo">
    <% if current_user %>
      <%= react_component("Menubutton") %>
      <a id="logo_anchor" href="/"><h1>Herpetology<span id="herpID">Pro</span></h1></a>
      <span>&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp</span>
    <% else %>
      <%= react_component("Menubutton") %>
      <a id='logo_anchor' href="/"><h1>Herpetology<span id="herpID">Pro</span></h1></a>
      <%= link_to 'Sign In/Up', '/users/sign_up', class: 'right_of_logo' %>
    <% end %>
  </div>
  <div id="menu" class="center drop_down_menu">
    <ul id="menu-inner">
      <li><h4><a href="/">Home</a></h4></li>
      <li><h4><%= link_to scoreboard_path do %>
          Scoreboard
          <% if current_user %>
            (<%= current_user.place_on_scoreboard.ordinalize %>)
          <% end %>

        <% end %>
      </h4></li>
      <% if current_user && current_user.admin_or_contributor? %>
        <li><h4><%= link_to reports_path do %>Reports(<%= Report.pending.size %>)
          <% end %></h4></li>
      <% end %>
      <li>
        <h4><%= link_to "https://github.com/n8ta/HerpID", target: '_blank' do %>HerpID on Github
          <% end %></h4><br/>
        <a class="github-button" href="https://github.com/n8ta/herpid/issues" data-icon="octicon-issue-opened" data-size="large" data-show-count="true" aria-label="Issue n8ta/herpid on GitHub">Issues</a><br/>
        <a class="github-button" href="https://github.com/n8ta/herpID" data-icon="octicon-star" data-size="large" data-show-count="true" aria-label="Star n8ta/herpID on GitHub">Star</a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h4>Developer: <%= link_to "https://n8ta.com/", target: '_blank' do %>Nate Tracy-Amoroso
          <% end %></h4>
      </li>
      <li>
        <% if current_user %>
          <h4>Settings</h4>
          <%= react_component('Settings', {show_dead: current_user.show_dead_photos}) %>
        <% else %>
          <H4>Settings</H4>
          <p>If you make an account you can toggle seeing photos of dead animals on and off as well as see statistics on
            accuracy.</p>
          <%= link_to "Signup", '/users/sign_up' %>
        <% end %>
      </li>
      <li><p>Do not use information learned here in life or death situations. All data on which species are venomous is crowdsourced and thus almost certainly incomplete and may be inaccurate (though people seem to be acting in good faith). When in ANY doubt leave a herp alone.</p></li>
      <li>
        <% unless current_user.nil? %>
          <h4>  <%= link_to destroy_user_session_path, method: :delete do %> Sign Out
            <% end %></h4>
        <% end %>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>


</div>
<div id="breadcrumb">
  <%= yield :breadcrumb %>
  <div id="subregions" class="drop_down_menu">
    <div id="subregions-inner">
      <%= yield :subregions %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="flash"><%= flash[:notice] %><%= flash[:alert] %></div>

<div id="content">
  <%= yield %>
</div>
</body>

</html>
